    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2f33351c0b6b7ec2344bc3d33b71e873.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友们一起享受疯狂与欢乐吧！齐心协力，完成各种任务，一路创造难忘的回忆，打造完美的加油站！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/18b2c958d9e7cb16fd590bb2f1e4f290.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级并定制你的加油站，让它变得更棒！扩展服务，打造属于你的独特风格，吸引更多顾客，赚取更多财富！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/f3233a62d7fab3d6bf69e345d29d9e30.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为顾客提供最佳的服务是我们的首要任务。我们的汽油品质一流，团队也同样优秀！给顾客带来难忘的体验，并享受丰厚的小费吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2750a9c33f893fe2ed2bb0d2a6c72040.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了便利店！顾客不仅要加油，他们还想买些东西！为他们提供最棒的商品。同时也要小心小偷（有时他们可是毫无礼貌的！）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2378a48acd0320da068d787ea617f4e0.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通往成功的道路不止一条——你还可以做兼职赚取额外收入！如果你足够自信，也可以试试刮刮卡碰碰运气！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>是的，有时候我们也想放下一切，开一家自己的加油站！</strong></p>",
